{"title":"非典的冠","authors":["成幼殊"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":7,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"非典的冠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成幼殊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小小的，看不见的冠冕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一滴水，落入油中，飞溅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是上苍的惩罚，对于污染，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破坏，千奇百怪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"或是自然的进程，探试"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类的坚韧、才智？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是地震、风暴、海啸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它飞飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却也不是气泡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是璀璨的王冠——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而像是那耶稣头戴的荆条。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫它非典，这简称，绝非昵爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少事，溢出于典型之外？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，怎样的全球阵容，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对人的关怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天使，白衣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出征在第一排。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的国家，古老又年轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再一度泡桐花姹紫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳、银杏青青。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众志刺破非典的冠，还靠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上上下下，以民为先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如抗震，如抗洪，排山倒海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华风采，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿从此，虚假，粉饰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被大步抛出九霄云外，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共庆胜中之胜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎未来。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":16,"page_end":16}